{"tid":2319980,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"動森劇場《黑心公司工作的我去了異世界當魔法師》","createTime":"2020-12-10T12:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T00:49:08.000Z","uid":129010,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a06d6a20a10e8aa6f8c9819fe585a1787a68efbe","tid":2319980,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TPyG1op8i-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTPyG1op8i-Q&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=69dc934b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TPyG1op8i-Q</a><br />\n<br />\n李成光這個故事的主人公，在一個名為香城的城市出生。大學畢業之後，加入了一間由狸克所成立黑心公司。雖然每日都好心機，但晚晚都要加班到深夜。有一次深夜回到家中，閉上眼後就去到一個不知名地方，遇到默脈，送往異世界重新開始。"},{"pid":"1a6967c190de0c7cffa0cb259aa7cde57623bf83","tid":2319980,"uid":162096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"4b77971e8402ffba770a3b0b141bcfaf29764616","tid":2319980,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6967c190de0c7cffa0cb259aa7cde57623bf83","tid":2319980,"uid":162096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:47:41.000Z","msg":"G持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:49:18.000Z","msg":"多謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a6e9d56df7f023958c0d556470af3e41d8b323","tid":2319980,"uid":85378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"f2a23db2c0ab34a4e4506c08c1e8501955c4fcc2","tid":2319980,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96a6e9d56df7f023958c0d556470af3e41d8b323","tid":2319980,"uid":85378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:54:40.000Z","msg":"留名先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaca9a4156a8acdbce393c048de7c867f6350760","tid":2319980,"uid":129010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:47:59.000Z","msg":"下集預告<br />\n阿光去到異世界之後沿住路牌去最近的村落。途中，突然遇到埋伏被一隻藍色棉羊捉了。在牢中，幸好在一個自稱魔法研究員查克協助下，阿光與他並肩逃脫棉羊的基地最難的機關「魔法密室」。<br />\n<br />\n截圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ys1Zzyu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYs1Zzyu.png&h=ea0698b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Rx6eyv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Rx6eyv.png&h=094b2eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8PPWMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8PPWMR.png&h=3c46555e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEQWBMR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEQWBMR.png&h=cd99e993&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2ccade223460837e73835ad2a639b9c3549e15f","tid":2319980,"uid":28759,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T17:37:22.000Z","msg":"想幫你配過條聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74d85794310f7b18c049f8241922e0429af2cb8","tid":2319980,"uid":25250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e79cfd9e4c5cb22b6684e739341a602b0a23e5","tid":2319980,"uid":129010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"第二集出咗啦！繁中字幕提供<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介：阿光去到異世界之後沿住路牌去最近的村落。途中，突然遇到埋伏被一隻藍色棉羊捉了。在牢中，幸好在一個自稱魔法研究員查克協助下，阿光與他並肩逃脫藍色棉羊的基地中最難的機關「魔法密室」。<br />\n<br />\nSynopsis: Captured by a blue sheep, the protagonist Jack Lee met Erik,  a magical researcher. In the mysterious base, there's a complicated chamber. With Erik, Jack was able to escape the magical chamber.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqQyGjQ0lSs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqQyGjQ0lSs&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpkcTp%2BQsjpNju